Overcoat

Protects the Pokémon from things like sand, hail, and powder.

Affected Moves

This ability protects against the following moves.

Name Type Category PP Power Accuracy Description
Cotton Spore 40 — 100 The user's cotton-like spores cling to opposing Pokémon, harshly lowering Speed stats.
Magic Powder 20 — 100 The user scatters a cloud of magic powder that changes the target to Psychic type.
Poison Powder 35 — 75 The user scatters a cloud of poisonous dust that poisons the target.
Powder 20 — 100 The target is covered in a combustible powder that explodes from Fire-type moves.
Rage Powder 20 — — The user scatters a cloud of irritating powder. Opposing Pokémon aim only at the user.
Sleep Powder 15 — 75 The user scatters a big cloud of sleep-inducing dust around the target.
Spore 15 — 100 The user scatters bursts of spores that induce sleep.
Stun Spore 30 — 75 The user scatters a cloud of numbing powder that paralyzes the target.
